    <h2>7. Limitation of liability</h2>
    <p>To the maximum extent permitted by law, the maintainers of ostk shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of the software or this website.</p>

    <h2>8. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update these terms. Changes will be posted to this page with an updated effective date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .meta {
    color: var(--ostk-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--ostk-text-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--ostk-space-8);
  }
  .meta a {
    color: var(--ostk-text-muted);
  }
  .meta a:hover {
    color: var(--ostk-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
